message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: anyclaude-sdk
abstract: >-
  Claude Code agent capabilities (tools, the tool loop, MCP, sub-agents,
  sessions) for any OpenAI- or Anthropic-compatible LLM endpoint, running in the
  browser (WebContainer), Node, and Bun — with a serverless "survivor",
  client-side tools, server-side prompt projection, and a React UI kit.
type: software
authors:
  - family-names: Ade
    given-names: Hans
license: MIT
repository-code: "https://github.com/pipilot-dev/anyclaude-sdk"
url: "https://anyclaude-docs.puter.site"
keywords:
  - claude
  - agent
  - llm
  - webcontainer
  - browser
  - ai
